00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,600
Just a little bit
different implementation for each one.

154
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:56,333
Now in Kubernetes I can do

155
00:07:56,333 --> 00:07:59,333
Kubernetes draining as well
when I'm draining,

156
00:07:59,633 --> 00:08:04,166
actual requests to spin up new instances.

